Package util

Class ElementFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • util.ElementFactory
  • public class ElementFactory
extends java.lang.Object

    ElementFactory

    This class is used as a factory to provide game elements to GameController's child class, including:

    1. NormalGameController;

    2. InfiniteGameController.

    The elements include:
    1. FroggerView;
    2. EndView;
    3. CarView;
    4. ShortTruckView;
    5. LongTruckView;
    6. SnakeView;
    7. CrocodileBodyView;
    8. CrocodileHeadView;
    9. LogView;
    10. WetTurtleView;
    11. DryTurtleView.

    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.3
    Author:
    Kejia Wu, scykw1@nottingham.ac.uk
    See Also:
    NormalGameController, InfiniteGameController, FroggerView, EndView
